column5: BREAKING NEWS! Wiarton Willie was found dead today from an apparent self-inflicted gunshot wound after predicting an early spring.
Nah ... that picture was pirated from our own Punxatawny Phil.

I am glad.   I love winter you just made my day, It is becoming a challenge to jump the truck from shore to get onto the 48 inches of ice .   Still lots of trout to catch,  may he rest in peace  , I will happily send flowers to the family,  or should I say nuts and vegetables, a few more weeks of no sandflies, blackflies and sweating,  but it is a waste of lead, a trap would have sufficed  lol, good post
The picture would be better if there were tire tracks over him too.
And a smouldering cigarette in the background.
i can guaruntee you that there are handguns around Wiarton, my grandfather owns 2 from the 1800's about 15 minutes outside of Wiarton   and thats an awesome pic lol
Not Wiarton Willie! Willie is an albino!
